---
title: Chicken Schnitzel Sandwiches with Gruyère and Tangy Red Cabbage Slaw
description: Traditionally this dish is made with breaded and fried veal cutlets. In our version, we’re butterflying chicken breasts before lightly dredging them in flour for a lighter preparation. Served under a blanket of gooey Gruyère and tangy cabbage, this sandwich is more than dinner-worthy.
